name: Living color dots #2
description:
Click to start with a different seed.

512x512px interactive

Living color dots is a series of pieces based on a rather complex game of life. Its represented by color pixels that try to move always in the same directions. The pixels try to expand while there is space available, and they try to coexist with the others or get extint. Often only a color survive at the end.
The waves you see happen as dots die and the children get born. There is no random behaviour (just for the initial conditions) there are only very simple rules.

In this version #2 the color pixels are similar to strokes of a brush.
